{"tid":711484,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好期待 全民造星","createTime":"2018-06-21T14:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T14:31:11.000Z","uid":168743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"005daaeb1cd30716d349039b165991e662551b40","tid":711484,"uid":168743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:31:11.000Z","msg":"[black]近日Viutv發佈選秀節目《全民造星》，面試選出99位「男神」後，大舉於網上進行投票環節。怎料99位「男神」的造型照剛「出街」，便引起一眾網民劣評，皆因99位男生悉數以黑白色作主調，造型過於統一，甚至令人想起旺角「Chic之堡」的衣著風格。不過造型以外，其實這些「男神」為數不少也是臥虎藏龍，才華爆燈，可惜卻被外型的話題性掩蓋。今日率先與大家分享一下，99位「男神」中略有名氣的音樂型才子。[/black]<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/21/223007_932ecfcbb05941ae38a336457a206940.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F21%2F223007_932ecfcbb05941ae38a336457a206940.png&h=8e6834d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/音樂/192834/viutv-全民造星-造型太-mk-埋沒咗幾多音樂才子\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%2F192834%2Fviutv-%E5%85%A8%E6%B0%91%E9%80%A0%E6%98%9F-%E9%80%A0%E5%9E%8B%E5%A4%AA-mk-%E5%9F%8B%E6%B2%92%E5%92%97%E5%B9%BE%E5%A4%9A%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82%E6%89%8D%E5%AD%90&d=rKuEXMB5T1WbgDAVYwUu1QhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2f902e53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/音樂/192834/viutv-全民造星-造型太-mk-埋沒咗幾多音樂才子</a><br />\n<br />\n真係好期待<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}